quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  11,6,"Alaa e ruugayngel ka leydi si wanah ko Alla fawtii arsike maggel on, Himo anndi ГұiiЙ“irde maggel e daakorde maggel; fow no e Deftere Й“anngunde"
  11,7,"Ko Kanko tagi kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin nder balЙ—e jeegoo, hari arsi Makko kin no ka hoore ndiyam, fii yo O ndaarndo on ko hommbo e mo'on Й“urata moЖҙЖҙinnde gollal. Pellet si a wi'i: \"Onon ko on ummintinteeЙ“e Й“aawo maayde\", maa heeferЙ“e Й“en wi'u: \"ЖҠum wonaali si wanaa mbilewu feeГұungu\". @Corrected"
  11,8,"Pellet si Men nennaniiЙ“e lepte Й—en haa e dumunna limaaЙ—o, maa Й“e wi'u: \"Ko tonngi Й—e?\" Anndee Гұalnde nde arat e mabЙ“e, Й“e wonataa sureteeЙ“e e majje; jippoo e maЙ“Й“e kon ko laatinoo hiЙ“e jalkita"
  11,9,"Si tawii Men meeЙ—inii neЙ—Й—anke on neema immornde ka Amen, refti Men Й“oori nde e makko, kanko ko otaЖҙaado, yeddoowo"
  11,10,"Si tawii kadi Men meeЙ—inirii mo neema Й“aawo lorra memuЙ—o mo, maa o wi'oy : \"Satteende nden iwii e am\", kanko (ontuma) ko o weltiiЙ—o, ГұaaГұoowo"
  11,11,"Si wanaa Й“en muГұГұii Й“e, Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe. ЖҒen Й—on, no woodani Й“e haforanal e njoЙ“di mawndi"
  11,12,"Belajo'o ko a accoowo yoga ko wahayinaa e maaЙ—a, Й“ernde maa nden Й“iЙ—tora Й—um; fii hiЙ“e wi'i: \"Ko haЙ—no ngalu jippinee e makko? maa Malaa'ikaajo arda e makko?\" Anndu an ko a jertinoowo. Alla ko deenoowa kala huunde"
  11,13,"Kaa Й“e wi'ay : \"O fefindi nde?\" Maaku : \"Addee Corteeji( cimooje) sappo yeru mayre, pepindaaЙ—e, noddon kala mo haЙ—tanЙ—on gaanin Alla, si on laatike goonguЙ“e"
  11,14,"Si Й“e jaabitaaki on, anndee wonnde ko nde jippinira ko ganndal Alla, e wonnde reweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa Kanko. Hara onon ko on jebbiliiЙ“e"
  11,15,"Kala on tawЙ—o ko nguurndam aduna e cuЙ—aari majjam faandii, Men humnanay Й“e golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en ton, hara kamЙ“e Й“e Й—uytantaake ton"
  11,16,"Ko Й“en woni Й“e alanah Й—um en ka laakara si wanaa Yiite. Ko Й“e golli ton kon firtii, ko meere woni koЙ“e gollaynoo"
  11,17,"E ko on laatiiЙ—o e Й“anngannduyee immorde ka Joomi makko, himo janngande mo seediiЙ—o immorde ka Makko, e nde aditiinde mo [kanko Muhammadu], Deftere Muusaa nden ardiinde e yurmeende [Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude diini ko alah hujja kon?]: ЖҒen Й—on hino gomЙ—ini nde; kala on yedduЙ—o nde e feddeeji Й—in, ko Yiite ngen woni fodoore makko. Wata a laato e sikke fii mayre. Pellet ko nde goonga immornde ka Joomi maa; ko woni tun, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en gomЙ—intaa"
  11,18,"Ko hommbo Й“uri tooГұude Й“uri on fefandiido fenaa- nde e hoore Alla? ЖҒen Й—on holliroyte ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e, (malaa'ikaaЙ“e) seediiЙ“e Й“en wi'a: \"Ko Й“ee Й—oo feni bakki e Joomi maЙ“Й“e\". Hey, kuddi Alla ndin wonii e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  11,19,"ЖҒen falotooЙ“e gaay e laawol Alla ngol, Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“ana ngol ooГұorde, hara kadi ko Й“e yedduЙ“e laakara"
  11,20,"ЖҒen Й“e wonaali laawotooЙ“e ka leydi, laatanaaki Й“e kadi weldiiЙ“e gaanin Alla, hiЙ“e sowoyanee lepte Й—en. ЖҒe laatanooki hattanЙ“e nanugol, Й“e wonaano kadi yi'ooЙ“e"
  11,21,Ko Й“e woni sooyinЙ“e wonkiiji mun Й—in. Kon ko Й“e fefintonoo majji gaay e maЙ“Й“e
  11,22,"Sikke alah, wonnde Й“en Й—on ka laakara, ko kamЙ“e Й“uroyta sooyude"
  11,23,"ЖҒen gonЙ—imЙ“e, Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe, Й“e yankinanii Joomi maЙ“Й“e, ko Й“e woni yimЙ“e Aljanna Й“en, kamЙ“e ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e ton"